title: Ep. - 505 - DIRECTOR OF ACCEPTED LUKE GULBRANSON FROM SUMMER HOUSE
description:
Kate discusses All Star Shore on Paramount + and the latest updates to the Chrisley Knows Best case.

 

Dan Chen, Director of Accepted, a documentary about four high school seniors in rural Louisiana attending T.M. Landry, an unconventional school housed in a warehouse made famous for sending its graduates to elite universities. Accepted gives a unique and intriguing look at the world of Ivy League college admissions and the true cost of getting that first foothold into elite American society.

 

Luke Gulbranson from Summer House on Bravo discusses not being asked back this season, who he will still keep in touch with, and whether he would like to do other Bravo spinoffs.
